Package: s7contract
Title: Go-Like Interfaces and Rust-Like Traits for 'S7'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Sounkou Mahamane", family = "Toure",
           email = "sounkoutoure@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Experimental contract helpers for 'S7'. The Go-like layer models
    basic structural interfaces as sets of required generics. The Rust-like
    layer adds explicit trait declarations, default methods, and associated
    metadata on top of ordinary 'S7' dispatch.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
Imports: S7
Suggests:
